'''Blogposium = simultaneous blogging on the same topic'''


=Definition=

"A blogposium allows those in the blogosphere to simultaneously blog on the same topic (OK - the word is new, the idea is not). It leverages the power of tagging and social bookmarking to provide an easy way for everyone to not only participate in but also to keep track of the conversation."
(http://www.technosight.com/blog/blogoposium-one/)


